OL,4,G1700F5 News with Dan Walker
OL,5,     GJoin Dan Walker and the team for
OL,6,     Gthe news that matters to you.
OL,7,G1800FLove Nature
OL,8,     GAt an aquarium in Portaferry, a
OL,9,     Gsmall group of penguins offer a
OL,10,     Gwindow into a bigger global story
OL,11,     Gabout these flightless birds.
OL,12,G1805FSusan Calman's Grand Day Out
OL,13,     GSusan follows Ross Poldark's
OL,14,     Gtrail in Cornwall: dancing in
OL,15,     GHelston, scything near Liskeard,
OL,16,     Gsailing in Falmouth, exploring
OL,17,     Gtin mining and the county's
OL,18,     Gwartime history - plus bagpipes!
